subject: Football
Governors (US)
Gambling
lead_paragraph: The governor of Pennsylvania is betting jams and wine, and his counterpart in New York is offering Nathan’s hot dogs and apple cider on the outcome of the A.F.C. championship game Sunday between the Pittsburgh Steelers and the Jets.
